   TEEPEN-COLUMN _ Even God can be absent-minded. God forgot _ just
flat forgot _ to clue Moses to the 11th Commandment: Thou shalt not
bow down to the National Rifle Association. (Tom Teepen is national
correspondent for Cox Newspapers.) MOVED MONDAY.
