<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-22 12:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5016 &Cx1f; tad-z
r w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CONGRESS-COST-DATA-$A     06-22 1380
</HEADER>
<BODY>
