and Timothy Leland. 1800 words.
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-CRUISE (Undated) _ While the war in Kosovo seems over and
peace may be at hand, it has taken its toll on the European cruise
season. By Jerry Morris. 1325 words.
</P>
