<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-22 14:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5163 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      06-22 1024
