Henry Cisneros admitted in Cisneros's fraud trial. The damaging
information was seen as an attempt to ``inoculate'' Cisneros's
former mistress against attacks by his defense lawyers, who start
cross-examining Jones later Tuesday. (Malone, Cox News Service).
18.
