<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-COX-CARIBBEAN-TRADE23 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SENATE PANEL VOTES TO EXPAND CARIBBEAN TRADE PREFERENCES
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By LARRY LIPMAN
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
