<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-22 16:37 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5330 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JESSE-JACKSON-HERO-NY     06-22 2271
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JESSE-JACKSON-HERO-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE JESSE FACTOR 
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;     (To publish this ``separate buy'' article, it must be purchased
_ the rate is not prohibitive _ from one of these New York Times
Syndicate sales representatives: 
