</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COCA-COLA WORLDWIDE MARKET SHARE
 &HT;    With LATAM-COKE-0622.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (f) Financial categories.
 &HT;    By SHELLEY EMLING 
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
<P>
   COKE ON A GLOBAL SCALE
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  25 percent of Coke's sales are in Latin America
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  21 percent are in Europe
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  19 percent are in the Middle and Far East
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  30 percent are in North America and Canada
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  5 percent are in various other countries.
</P>
<P>
   COKE vs PEPSI: South of the Border
</P>
<P>
   Argentina.........................Coke 62.5 percent.......Pepsi
30 percent
</P>
<P>
   Brazil.................................Coke 52.1
percent.......Pepsi 7.2 percent
</P>
<P>
   Mexico...............................Coke 67
percent...........Pepsi 20 percent
</P>
<P>
   Venezuela........................Coke 68.6 percent.......Pepsi
13.2 percent
</P>
<P>
   Colombia..........................Coke 58.5 percent.......Pepsi
8.1 percent
</P>
<P>
   United States................Coke 44.5 percent........Pepsi 31.4
percent
</P>
