company. Now, as the landscape keeps changing, it's wondering if
that is enough? BellSouth, Qwest, Global Crossing, US West and
Frontier.... How will this all shake out? What are the stakes for
BellSouth? What are the options? (Kanell, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 30.
</P>
