One miunute, the game is there; the next minute it's gone. Mark
Wohlers, Ian Baker-Finch, Scott Norwood, Steve Sax and Dale Murphy,
to name a few, cannot provide answers why their games suddenly
disappeared. But sports shrinks provide a number of scenarios.
(Pasquarelli, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
