 San Francisco _ PERGOLAS _  Call it a pergola, call it an arbor,
call it _ if you must _ a shade structure. By any name, a
vine-covered outdoor dining area is an appealing feature of many
gardens. With filtered sunlight dappling the table and the scent of
jasmine wafting down, a summer lunch under a pergola can be a
sensual feast.
