<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-22 19:36 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5600 &Cx1f; tad-z
u p &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BUSH23-1STLEDE-COX     06-22 0969
