<HEADLINE>
CLINTON THANKS U.S. PILOTS WHO FLEW OVER KOSOVO 
</HEADLINE>
   (bl)  
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   AVIANO AIR BASE, Italy _ On the last stop of his six-day
European trip, President Clinton thanked the members of the U.S.
31st Air Expeditionary Wing whose pilots flew many of the missions
over Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
   ``Thank you for turning back the tide of ethnic cleansing,''
Clinton said.
</P>
</TEXT>
