<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-WYO.-MED-SCHOOL-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   WYO.-MED-SCHOOL (Undated) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, June 22. &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
