 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-TEN-WIMBLEDON-HINGIS-NYT, which
moved in ``s'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``I guess I still can't believe I've beaten her.''
</P>
<P>
   _JALENA DOKIC, 16 and ranked No. 129 in the world in tennis,
after ousting top-ranked Martina Hingis at Wimbledon.
</P>
</TEXT>
